{"meta":{"title":"Morôni 2","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/2?lang=por","contentType":"text/html","audio":[{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ//2013-06-253-moroni-02-64k-por.mp3","voice":{"name":"audio"}}],"pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"70e5e6a476d92445d6ed59828c2b5204fcde67e9","data-aid":"124207471","data-aid-version":"3","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/2","itemscope":"","itemtype":"http://schema.org/Article","lang":"por","data-orig-id":"c528b9ff04433774f8e0ccd008b533bfe32b89cb","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"Morôni 2","description":"Jesus deu poder aos doze discípulos nefitas para conferirem o Espírito Santo. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C."},"pageSocial":{"title":"Morôni 2","description":"Jesus deu poder aos doze discípulos nefitas para conferirem o Espírito Santo. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"124207487\" id=\"title_number1\">Capítulo 2</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"124207488\" id=\"study_summary1\">Jesus deu poder aos doze discípulos nefitas para conferirem o Espírito Santo. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124207489\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>As palavras que Cristo disse a seus <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>discípulos</a>, os doze por ele escolhidos, quando lhes impôs as mãos —</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124207490\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>E chamou-os pelo nome, dizendo: Invocareis o Pai em meu nome, em fervorosa oração; e depois que tiverdes feito isso, tereis <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>poder</a> para <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>conferir</a> o Espírito Santo àqueles sobre quem impuserdes as <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note2c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>mãos</a>; e em meu nome conferi-lo-eis, pois assim fazem os meus apóstolos.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124207491\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>Ora, Cristo disse-lhes estas palavras quando apareceu pela primeira vez; e a multidão não as ouviu, mas ouviram-nas os discípulos; e a todos sobre quem <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>impuseram</a> as mãos, desceu o Espírito Santo.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124207492\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/13.25?lang=por#p25\">3 Né. 13:25</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"2\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note2a\" data-full-marker=\"2a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124207493\" id=\"note2a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/power?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Poder</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note2b\" data-full-marker=\"2b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124207494\" id=\"note2b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/18.37?lang=por#p37\">3 Né. 18:37</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note2c\" data-full-marker=\"2c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124207495\" id=\"note2c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/hands-laying-on-of?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Mãos, Imposição de</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note3a\" data-full-marker=\"3a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124207496\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/nt/acts/19.6?lang=por#p6\">At. 19:6</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","associated":{"p1":[{"sizes":"250px","alt":"O Dom do Espírito Santo","aspectRatio":"0.6666666666666666","height":"480","width":"320","missingAsset":"false","assetId":"8e69acda5ab2b8d3a856e4397c574500984fd277","srcset":"https://assets.ldscdn.org/45/b8/45b82cd654d20eb44f4cf443d1fa3579aaf73212/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 60w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/11/d2/11d2be5412ff4da00064b0aafa623543f4a33c40/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 100w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/35/08/35089306a99a1a2ab76ca53d06901937a867f6ee/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 200w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/6c/e8/6ce85734371a445c93d5122dfa82803d2acd2a15/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 250w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/58/c7/58c7a81027d5dc120e539da690f7e25c4c5809b4/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 320w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/26/1f/261f2b4e9f5b75066cfa5c39057e94325460e27a/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 500w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/37/e5/37e59429886368b873cce4c15e1e7367852e0d36/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 640w","imgId":"8e69acda5ab2b8d3a856e4397c574500984fd277","src":"https://assets.ldscdn.org/58/c7/58c7a81027d5dc120e539da690f7e25c4c5809b4/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg","id":"aside1_img1","altSource":"https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/media/image/girl-being-confirmed-8e69acd","attribs":{"data-alt-source":"https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org/media/image/girl-being-confirmed-8e69acd","id":"aside1_img1","src":"https://assets.ldscdn.org/58/c7/58c7a81027d5dc120e539da690f7e25c4c5809b4/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg","data-img-id":"8e69acda5ab2b8d3a856e4397c574500984fd277","srcset":"https://assets.ldscdn.org/45/b8/45b82cd654d20eb44f4cf443d1fa3579aaf73212/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 60w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/11/d2/11d2be5412ff4da00064b0aafa623543f4a33c40/girl_being_confirmed.jpeg 100w,https://assets.ldscdn.org/35/08/3508